# IntelliJ / Android Studio per-user state. The previous list of
# specific .idea/* entries (caches, libraries, workspace.xml, …) only
# covered some of the files the IDE writes; per-developer files like
# compiler.xml, gradle.xml, markdown.xml, misc.xml, runConfigurations.xml
# and vcs.xml ended up tracked anyway and got committed by the IDE on
# every developer's checkout (issue #7). Excluding the whole `.idea/`
# tree is the standard JetBrains recommendation.
.idea/
.DS_Store
/build
/captures
.externalNativeBuild
.cxx
local.properties
